Text: OTCWelcomes OTC Attendees Please visit our website for the BEST networking tool of the year You can EMail directly from our searchable database both US International Offshore Oil and Gas Company contacts as well as the Offshore Technology attendees wwwglobaltradedayscom then click on bottom righthand corner for easy searching or simply download the list of over of last years attendees in Adobe Acrobat Reader format While in downtown Houston come to our cybercaf for a cappuccino or a cup of coffee at Allen Center Smith St Suite and check your EMail in comfort To learn more about how Global Trade Days can help you grow your business give Hal McClure a call at Or EMail Network with the Best wwwglobaltradedayscom
